We need to enact pipeline safety reauthorization legislation before the end of this Congress.  A lot of work has gone into the current bills, and there are no major disagreements about what a compromise among the various bills should look like.  Let\'92s get a good bill passed now.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}
