The Pipeline Safety Improvement Act of 2002 is a success.  Industry and DOT have cooperated to achieve significant improvement in pipeline safety, and this improvement is demonstrated by our industry\'92s record.  This record is reflected on the charts that accompany my testimony.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\fs24 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\'95	}
